track_notes:
Easy track till the Colle, then is a rocky trail.
Is a double summit North Peak is higher than South peak. I do both, pay attention in case of wet and slippery rocks.
Bel sentiero in ombra al mattino salendo dopo il bivio per il Selleries.  Al pomeriggio salgono quasi sempre le nuvole di condensa.
track_title: class E ,  good track, phone OK , rocky  summit
